{"id": "25188", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25188", "title": "Quaid", "text": "Quaid is a confused &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt; who continuously talks about his journey taking a fortnight, and eventually explodes in a fireball if continued talking to him.\nBackground.\nThe entire sequence of events is a reference to the movie Total Recall, specifically a scene where the main character, Douglas Quaid, is disguised as a woman trying to pass through Mars customs. The disguise malfunctions, and can only repeat the phrase \"two weeks\" (a fortnight), and eventually explodes, killing a security officer and causing an explosive decompression."}
