{"id": "56592", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56592", "title": "GHOST3.ITM", "text": "GHOST3.ITM is an undroppable ring that grants immunities and various visual effects to certain creatures in the game, such as &lt;a href=\"Aurumach%20Rilmani\"&gt;Aurumach Rilmani&lt;/a&gt; found on the &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep%20Final%20Seal\"&gt;Watcher's Keep Final Seal&lt;/a&gt; dungeon level.\nThis item provides 100% &lt;a href=\"Magical%20damage\"&gt;Magical damage&lt;/a&gt; resistance.\nIt also bestows a pulsing glow cosmetic appearance to the creature's sprite.\nThe item implements several &lt;a href=\"IESDP\"&gt;IESDP&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Opcode\"&gt;Opcode&lt;/a&gt; 9 \"Color Glow Pulse\" effects, to make the creature look \"unearthly\" and partially intangible."}
{"id": "56415", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56415", "title": "GHOSTEFF.ITM", "text": "GHOSTEFF.ITM is an undroppable item equipped by various creatures that are to render a \"blurry\" or \"ghostly\" semi-transparent cosmetic appearance. \nAlthough the item is a ring, it can be placed in other slots by the game engine (such as a helmet or amulet). It does not affect the item's applied effects.\nThe item actually applies &lt;a href=\"IESDP\"&gt;IESDP&lt;/a&gt; effect codes number 65 \"Transparency Fade\", and several iterations of number 9 \"Color Glow Pulse\"."}
{"id": "49444", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49444", "title": "GHOUL1.ITM", "text": "GHOUL1.ITM is an undroppable weapon equipped to &lt;a href=\"Ghoul\"&gt;Ghoul&lt;/a&gt;s in the Weapon 1 slot.\nEffects.\nIt is considered a non-magical, non-enchanted weapon and deals 1d6 (no Strength bonus) with a range of one foot and a speed factor of three.\nEach successful hit upon a living target forces a &lt;a href=\"Saving%20throw\"&gt;save vs paralyze&lt;/a&gt; to negate a &lt;a href=\"Paralyze\"&gt;Paralyze&lt;/a&gt; effect for 30 seconds (Op Code 109). The effect can be dispelled and does not bypass resistance. The portrait of a paralyzed character will display a \"Held\" icon for the duration."}
{"id": "49286", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49286", "title": "GHOULLOR.ITM", "text": "GHOULLOR.ITM is an undroppable weapon used exclusively by &lt;a href=\"Ghoul%20Lord\"&gt;Ghoul Lords&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffects.\nThe Ghoul \"Lord\" Touch delivered by this item is a more powerful melee attack than the average &lt;a href=\"GHOUL1.ITM\"&gt;Ghoul Touch&lt;/a&gt;.\nFor the purposes of what it can it, it is considered a &lt;a href=\"Magical%20item\"&gt;magical&lt;/a&gt; weapon of &lt;a href=\"Enchanted%20item\"&gt;enchantment&lt;/a&gt; level two, with a range of one foot, and a speed factor of three.\nBesides dealing 1d6 damage to a living creature upon a successful hit, it has the following effects, none of which offer a saving throw, but all of which can be dispelled, do not bypass resistance, and have a duration of 100 seconds:\nIn addition, a &lt;a href=\"dwarf\"&gt;dwarf&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"half-elf\"&gt;half-elf&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"halfling\"&gt;halfling&lt;/a&gt; or human target must &lt;a href=\"Saving%20throw\"&gt;save vs death&lt;/a&gt; to avoid being &lt;a href=\"Paralyze\"&gt;Paralyzed&lt;/a&gt; for 30 seconds. A status message of \"Paralyzed\" appears in the UI, and a \"Held\" portrait icon is added to the affected character."}
{"id": "55733", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55733", "title": "GIAFIR.ITM", "text": "GIANFIR.ITM is an undroppable one-handed war hammer melee weapon used by the some &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Giant\"&gt;Fire Giant&lt;/a&gt; creatures.\nIt is considered a magical and +3 enchanted attack and deals 2d10 &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20damage\"&gt;Crushing damage&lt;/a&gt; plus 1d6 &lt;a href=\"Fire%20damage\"&gt;Fire damage&lt;/a&gt;]] (adjusted by &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; modifier), with a range of two feet, and speed factor of 7. \nThe weapon bestows a 3 point &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; bonus to hit.\nThe applied fire damage is of the non-magical type and will bypass &lt;a href=\"Magic%20resistance\"&gt;Magic resistance&lt;/a&gt; and spell &lt;a href=\"Power%20level\"&gt;Power level&lt;/a&gt; protections such as &lt;a href=\"Globe%20of%20Invulnerability\"&gt;Globe of Invulnerability&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Trap\"&gt;Spell Trap&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe item has no other abilities."}
