{"id": "7912", "revid": "3234315", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7912", "title": "Garan", "text": "Garan is a &lt;a href=\"mage/thief\"&gt;mage/thief&lt;/a&gt; who, on his teleport trip from &lt;a href=\"Maztica\"&gt;Maztica&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Waterdeep\"&gt;Waterdeep&lt;/a&gt;, got trapped on the &lt;a href=\"Ice%20Island\"&gt;Ice Island&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nGaran insists in being the one who poses the questions here, and has little patience with ignorant or joking people. No matter how the conversation with him goes \u2013 in the end he will always become hostile and will summon his four \"pet\" &lt;a href=\"Ankheg\"&gt;Ankheg&lt;/a&gt;s to make the fight an interesting one.\nTrivia.\nIn \"Tales of the Sword Coast:\""}
{"id": "7824", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7824", "title": "Garclax", "text": "Garclax is a chaotic &lt;a href=\"chaotic%20neutral\"&gt;neutral&lt;/a&gt; / &lt;a href=\"chaotic%20evil\"&gt;chaotic evil&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Gnoll%20Chieftain\"&gt;Gnoll Chieftain&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28game%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;\". He is the leader of a small band of &lt;a href=\"Gnoll\"&gt;Gnoll&lt;/a&gt;s who are detained within a &lt;a href=\"Bandit%20Camp%20Cave\"&gt;cave&lt;/a&gt; due to poor behavior in the &lt;a href=\"Bandit%20Camp\"&gt;Bandit Camp&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpon entering the cave, &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and party are attacked by the group after a brief bit of dialogue from Garclax. This surprisingly does not turn the rest of the camp hostile."}
