{"id": "34771", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=34771", "title": "Gardush", "text": "Gardush is one of six servants of &lt;a href=\"Sarevok%20Anchev\"&gt;Sarevok&lt;/a&gt;, all of whom are located on the fifth floor of the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Throne%20Headquarters\"&gt;Iron Throne Headquarters&lt;/a&gt; and are under orders from Sarevok to eliminate &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt; permanently. He will most likely be encountered during the quest &lt;a href=\"Investigating%20the%20Iron%20Throne\"&gt;Investigating the Iron Throne&lt;/a&gt; and will fight alongside &lt;a href=\"Zhalimar%20Cloudwulfe\"&gt;Zhalimar Cloudwulfe&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Aasim\"&gt;Aasim&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Alai\"&gt;Alai&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Diyab\"&gt;Diyab&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Naaman\"&gt;Naaman&lt;/a&gt;, and a &lt;a href=\"doppelganger\"&gt;doppelganger&lt;/a&gt; (in the guise of &lt;a href=\"Emissary%20Tar\"&gt;Emissary Tar&lt;/a&gt;).\nWhen &lt;a href=\"Charmed\"&gt;Charmed&lt;/a&gt;, Gardush has nothing to say.\nGameplay.\nGardush has very high strength, but is otherwise a straightforward fighter, lacking any enchanted gear or special tricks up his sleeve.\nIn combat he will simply attempt to engage the nearest party member in melee."}
