{"id": "11021", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11021", "title": "Ghast", "text": "Ghasts are more dangerous versions of &lt;a href=\"ghoul\"&gt;ghoul&lt;/a&gt;s, capable of not only &lt;a href=\"Paralyze\"&gt;paralyzing&lt;/a&gt; opponents like their lesser kin but also causing them to feel &lt;a href=\"Status%20Effects%23Negative\"&gt;nauseated&lt;/a&gt;. When more than one is encountered, they can be quite dangerous to very low-level parties and are best fought with ranged weapons and spells. "}
