{"id": "41368", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41368", "title": "Gilded Rope", "text": "The Gilded Rope is offered by &lt;a href=\"Visaj\"&gt;Visaj&lt;/a&gt; and allows access to &lt;a href=\"Deirex%27s%20Tower\"&gt;Deirex's Tower&lt;/a&gt;. This is part of the &lt;a href=\"Intrigue%20with%20Jarlaxle\"&gt;Intrigue with Jarlaxle&lt;/a&gt; side quest. Obtaining the rope and using it to enter &lt;a href=\"Deirex%27s%20Tower\"&gt;Deirex's Tower&lt;/a&gt; is the only way to further the questline.\nGameplay.\nObtaining the rope is an optional action for the party. \nWhen Visaj makes his proposal about this item, offering it for sale - the party can just reply via dialogue selection that it isn't interested. \nVisaj will remain in his location and if the party changes its mind later, can speak with him again and work through the dialogue to obtain the rope.\nAfter the questline is completed, the rope is taken back by &lt;a href=\"Jarlaxle\"&gt;Jarlaxle&lt;/a&gt;."}
