{"id": "24077", "revid": "46775035", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24077", "title": "Goblinoid", "text": "Goblinoid is a term used to refer collectively to and their various relative species, including &lt;a href=\"hobgoblin\"&gt;hobgoblin&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"bugbear\"&gt;bugbear&lt;/a&gt;s. The term can seem somewhat arbitrary, as certain creatures that are visually or culturally similar to goblins, such as &lt;a href=\"xvart\"&gt;xvart&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"tasloi\"&gt;tasloi&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"kobold\"&gt;kobold&lt;/a&gt;s, are not considered part of the goblinoid family tree."}
