{"id": "46615", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46615", "title": "Pheirkas's Home", "text": "Pheirkas's Home is the home of the dwarf &lt;a href=\"Pheirkas\"&gt;Pheirkas&lt;/a&gt; and is located on the end of a row of three houses that are situated between &lt;a href=\"Entar%20Silvershield%27s%20Estate\"&gt;Entar Silvershield's Estate&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Degrodel%27s%20Home\"&gt;Degrodel's Home&lt;/a&gt;. The front door is unlocked.\nPheirkas can be found standing in the foyer on the ground floor. The chest is locked with a DC of 30 and contains 6 .\nOn the second floor a sleeping woman is present at night. The nightstand next to the sleeping woman contains 5 and the other one is empty. The chest is locked with a DC of 40 and contains &lt;a href=\"Leather%20Armor\"&gt;Leather Armor&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shield\"&gt;Small Shield&lt;/a&gt;."}
